{"tid":1875660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大萬錦市議員嘲笑香港示威者並表示對人權冇興趣，政府堅持升中國國旗","createTime":"2020-02-12T02:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T17:44:46.000Z","uid":256837,"like":14,"dislike":190,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"9f613ecabaaf64cc2fbe323e859f3dfa8231e7a3","tid":1875660,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:20:29.000Z","msg":"事緣：<br />\n蝗蟲係加拿大civic Center 升國旗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628014</a><br />\n<br />\n【Chinada】加拿大萬錦市議會堅持升中國國旗，與當地居民背道而馳<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1873903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1873903</a><br />\n<br />\n萬錦市政府一個委員會，以6票對5票，通過提交改變市政大樓外掛上其他國家國旗的動議，而動議已排期在周二（11日）在市議會進行最終投票表決。根據萬錦市第五區市議員Andrew Keyes在區內所做的調查，反對繼續舉辦升旗儀式的人高達87%，只有10%的人支持繼續舉辦升旗儀式。<br />\n<br />\n經過6個鐘頭嘅辯論，最後5-8通過唔到，加拿大撚認住投no嘅議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSeoUy2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSeoUy2.jpg&h=f621c95f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dynamicmedia.zuza.com/zz/m/original_/0/c/0cbe4ffe-c0a5-47ad-8de8-a73750a31552/PIC-Regional_Councillor_Joe_Li___Super_Portrait.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdynamicmedia.zuza.com%2Fzz%2Fm%2Foriginal_%2F0%2Fc%2F0cbe4ffe-c0a5-47ad-8de8-a73750a31552%2FPIC-Regional_Councillor_Joe_Li___Super_Portrait.jpg&h=64ce1c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中最正嘅係呢位叫Joe Li議員嘅言論，嘲笑香港示威者，而且同佢講人權佢冇興趣聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oA4kcmp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoA4kcmp.png&h=cd079b20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ade3bb6502c9566cc93105769c27e6f4a6b3129","tid":1875660,"uid":191926,"like":301,"dislike":0,"score":301,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"仲好  升下旗又唔會對我地有咩影響<br />\n繼續比海外支那人搞大場鬧劇<br />\n<br />\n大多數人反對都繼續升<br />\n反而令中國威脅論 更容易發酵<br />\n<br />\n中國近十年呢種進攻性外效策略<br />\n只會自挖墳墓<br />\n<br />\nWHO，國際刑警 <br />\n呢堆部署左好耐的針  已經被習近平玩爛"},{"pid":"455dfdd2c000d6e8e9dacd184a4129f17039671d","tid":1875660,"uid":76365,"like":174,"dislike":0,"score":174,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"87%反對都過到，佢個市議會係咩構造？"},{"pid":"f8928c1502b71050f12e7ae4fd2dfd98814d9f78","tid":1875660,"uid":19353,"like":94,"dislike":0,"score":94,"quote":{"pid":"455dfdd2c000d6e8e9dacd184a4129f17039671d","tid":1875660,"uid":76365,"like":174,"dislike":0,"score":174,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"87%反對都過到，佢個市議會係咩構造？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"Made in Chi Na"},{"pid":"9e624bdfe287e149f9fb94977b7f1031fdb32877","tid":1875660,"uid":264433,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"幾年前好似有數據話Markham 93% 支那人 不意外"},{"pid":"f35304859efdcf088cca2171fb26dd4f9b372199","tid":1875660,"uid":256837,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"9e624bdfe287e149f9fb94977b7f1031fdb32877","tid":1875660,"uid":264433,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"幾年前好似有數據話Markham 93% 支那人 不意外"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:37:47.000Z","msg":"有45%華人包埋香港，台灣同中國。呢個動議有香港人提出"},{"pid":"939816ae1bbfcd02fd162974d97d81d3b520d589","tid":1875660,"uid":256837,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"455dfdd2c000d6e8e9dacd184a4129f17039671d","tid":1875660,"uid":76365,"like":174,"dislike":0,"score":174,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"87%反對都過到，佢個市議會係咩構造？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:41:52.000Z","msg":"嗰度好多大陸人地產商起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26830a4566bdb786dc00c7af0f4dfdd1385154d","tid":1875660,"uid":49588,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"加拿大政府做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/face